DescriptionPaper: {
	DisplayName: Description Paper
	Tooltip:
		'''
		This note is just to let you know that the Lostbelt Journey mod has added a new class: the Executor.
		However, since the mod currently lacks sufficient armor sprites, the mod provides Executor-modified versions of the vanilla armors listed below.
		[i:RainHat][i:RainCoat]Raincoat Set – crafted with [i:Silk]Silk
		[i:FishCostumeMask][i:FishCostumeShirt][i:FishCostumeFinskirt]Fish Costume Set – crafted with [i:ShadowScale]Shadow Scale/[i:TissueSample]Tissue Sample and [i:Bass]Bass, or transformed after defeating the evil biome boss
		[i:CowboyHat][i:CowboyJacket][i:CowboyPants] Cowboy Set – crafted with [i:ShadowScale] Shadow Scale / [i:TissueSample] Tissue Sample and [i:Silk] Silk
		[i:RuneHat][i:RuneRobe]Rune Wizard Set – crafted with [i:UnicornHorn]Unicorn Horn, [i:PixieDust]Pixie Dust, [i:SoulofLight]Soul of Light, and [i:Robe]Robe
		[i:FloretProtectorHelmet][i:FloretProtectorChestplate][i:FloretProtectorLegs]Floret Protector Set – can be transformed after defeating The Lifebringer
		[i:MonkBrows][i:MonkShirt][i:MonkPants]Monk Armor / [i:MonkAltHead][i:MonkAltShirt][i:MonkAltPants]Shinobi Armor – also receive Executor versions
		All of the reworked vanity sets mentioned above gain brand new effects and set bonuses.
		'''
}

